snippet.title: Poor Amber Heard! Media Portrayal is UNFAIR, Says The Independent.
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is looking pretty bad in during testimony for the Johnny Depp v The Sun case. But some media outlets say it's really UNFAIR, because she's not the one who is actually on trial... The Sun is.
